CurriculumVitae
DrPiyiDu,Male,aProfessorofMaterialsScienceandEngineeringatZhejiangUniversityHangzhouChina.HejoinedZhejiangUniversityin1992,wasasapostdoctoralresearchfellowinPhysicsDepartmentin1992,promotedtoAssociateprofessorin1994,andthentofullprofessorin1998.HereceivedaPhDandM.ScinMaterialsScienceandEngineeringfromZhejiangUniversityin1992and1987respectivelyandaB.ScinJinanUniversity(ShandongInstituteofBuildingMaterials)in1982JinanChina.From1998to1999,HewasavisitingscholaratUniversityofAveiroPortugal.
Hisprimaryresearchareasaresynthesisandprocessingofceramicthinandthickfilmsandceramicbulksincludingelectronicceramicsandfilms,semiconductorthinfilmsandtheirapplications,optic,electricandmagneticsensitivethinandthickfilms,anumberoffunctionalcompositethinandthickfilmsandcompositebulks,developmentofsmartmaterialsandsystems.Heisundertakingthemainprojectsof&ldquo;ferroelectric/ferromagneticcompositeceramicswithsuperhighpermittivityandhighpermeability&rdquo;,&ldquo;microwavematerialswithtunabledielectricconstant&rdquo;,&ldquo;selfinducedmetalsilisidenanowirespreparedbyCVDmethodwithoutcatalyst&rdquo;and&ldquo;dielectricthinfilm/nanowireelectrodeintegrativefunctionalstructureandapplications&rdquo;inresentyears.
Heisteachingthe2ndyear&quot;EssentialofMaterialsScience&quot;,the3rdyear&quot;MaterialsCrystalChemistry&quot;,andgraduatecourse&quot;EssentialofNon-crystallineMaterials&quot;.
HereceivedsecondgradeNationalAward,firstgradeProvincialAwardandsecondgradeEducationalMinistryAwardoftheadvancementofScienceandTechnologyforhisachievementintheresearchareas.Hehasauthoredover180publicationstypicallyinjournalsofANGEWANDTECHEMIE-INTERNATIONALEDITION,ADVANCEDMATERIALS,APPLIEDPHYSICSLETTERS,JOURNALOFMATERIALSCHEMISTRY,CRYSTALGROWTHANDDESIGN,JOURNALOFPHYSICALCHEMISTRY,NanotechnologyandJOURNALOFAPPLIEDPHYSICSetc,writtenabook,EssentialofMaterialsScienceandhadmorethanthirtyChinaPatentslicensed.HeisamemberofChineseCeramicSociety,amemberofChineseVacuumSocietyandamemberofChineseMechanicalEngineeringSociety.Heismembersoftheeditorialboardsof&ldquo;JournalofZhejiangUniversity-EngineeringScience&rdquo;,&ldquo;CeramicsScienceandArt&rdquo;and&ldquo;JournalofFunctionalMaterials&rdquo;andanassociateeditorof&quot;JournalofMaterialsScienceandEngineering&quot;
